snippet.title: Thalassophobia Simulator and Survival Horror Game, Full Fathom
snippet.description:
We're making an underwater survival horror game / thalassophobia simulator. It revolves around maintaining a derelict sub as it travels across an otherworldly sea.

Follow the dev progress : https://eirye.carrd.co/
